# Project Zero — Extraction Rule (Perfect-for-now)

## Source of truth
- Raw thoughts live in `raw/YYYY/MM/DD/HHMM.txt`
- Raw thoughts are immutable: NEVER edit or rewrite anything inside `raw/`

## Idempotency / processed tracker
- Tracker file: `state/processed_raw.txt`
- Process ONLY raw files whose path is NOT listed (exact match) in `state/processed_raw.txt`
- After successfully processing a raw file, append its path as a new line to `state/processed_raw.txt`
- Never duplicate outputs for already-processed raw files

